text: Logan Phillip Henderson (born September 14, 1989) is an American actor and singer. He is known for playing the role of Logan Mitchell on the Nickelodeon series Big Time Rush. Disney Channel series Pair of Kings. He is a current member of the band Big Time Rush. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:American pop singers Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Texas Category:Singers from Texas Category:Big Time Rush members Category:People from Temple, Texas
